---
title: Easy Peasy Chicken Tetrazzini with Linguine
description: Juicy Italian-seasoned chicken takes centre stage and tops tonight's creamy masterpiece! Rounding out the cast of characters are the garlicky cream sauce, fresh chopped tomatoes, spinach and caramelized onions...need we say more!
